To find an item click on the "Find on this page" button, enter the product number or the name or part of the name, and press enter.
If any matches are found it will take you to the first one, you can use the < and > buttons in the "Find Window" to navigate thru the "found" items.
Found items will be highlighted in Green or Blue.
When you find the one that you want click on the link to the right to go to that item.

Click on any of the column headings below to sort on that column

Each column has 3 options, Red down arrow for ascending sort, Red up arrow for descending sort, or NO arrow for no sort.

Using these sort options, you can sort on one or more columns.
